Package es.unizar.eina.T213_camping.utils

package es.unizar.eina.T213_camping.utils
Utility classes providing common functionality across the application.

Package Contents:

  • DateUtils - Date manipulation and validation utilities
  • DialogUtils - Dialog creation and management utilities
  • PriceUtils - Price calculation and formatting utilities
  • ReservationUtils - Reservation management utilities

Subpackages:

  • es.unizar.eina.T213_camping.utils.ModelUtils - Model-related utility classes
  • es.unizar.eina.T213_camping.utils.TestUtils - Testing utility classes
These utilities provide reusable functionality for:
  • Date handling and validation
  • User interface dialogs
  • Price calculations
  • Reservation operations
  • Model data manipulation
  • Testing support
